author: Connor Creates
description:
did I mention that it was one of the most amazing things I've ever seen?

This 3 month journey was full of challenges, and was honestly a roller coaster of emotions haha! but I definitely learned a lot and I'm proud I was able to accomplish my goal of raising a caterpillar into a butterfly!

Come say hi on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/itsconnorcreates
And subscribe here on YT: youtube.com/@itsConnorCreates

I really appreciate you taking the time to watch this video! It truly means a lot, so thank you! :) 

Check out Save Our Monarchs for more info:
https://www.saveourmonarchs.org/?srsltid=AfmBOooa9D3d9w92Mk9nhIKd_PPi2I8mdYnu16DNAmeZYu6RwEah-E3F

title: I Raised Caterpillars into Butterflies (28 Day Evolution)
